{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 13,
  "title": "第十三章（厭恥）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "寵辱若驚，"
    },
    {
      "text": "貴大患若身。"
    },
    {
      "text": "何謂寵辱。"
    },
    {
      "text": "辱為下，"
    },
    {
      "text": "得之若驚，"
    },
    {
      "text": "失之若驚，"
    },
    {
      "text": "是謂寵辱若驚。"
    },
    {
      "text": "何謂貴大患若身。"
    },
    {
      "text": "吾所以有大患者，為吾有身。"
    },
    {
      "text": "及吾無身，吾何有患。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故貴以身為天下者，則可寄天下，"
    },
    {
      "text": "愛以身為天下，若可託天下。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "身寵亦驚，身辱亦驚。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "貴，畏也。若，至也。謂大患至身，故皆驚。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "問何謂寵，何謂辱。寵者尊榮，辱者恥辱。及身還自問者，以曉人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "辱為下賤。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "得寵榮驚者，處高位如臨深危也。貴不敢驕，富不敢奢。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "失者，失寵處辱也。驚者，恐禍重來也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "解上得之若驚，失之若驚。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "復還自問：何故畏大患至身。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "吾所以有大患者，為吾有身。有身憂者，勤勞念其飢寒，觸情從慾，則遇禍患也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "使吾無有身體，得道自然，輕舉昇雲，出入無間，與道通神，當有何患。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言人君貴其身而賤人，欲為天下主者，則可寄立，不可以久也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言人君能愛其身，非為己也，乃欲為萬民之父母。以此得為天下主者，乃可以託其身於萬民之上，長無咎也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
